</description><guid isPermaLink="false">https://www.thefarside.com/2026/07/09/1</guid><pubDate>Thu, 09 Jul 2026 08:06:00 -0400</pubDate></item><item><title>The Far Side - 2026-07-09 #1</title><link>https://www.thefarside.com/2026/07/09/0</link><description>&lt;div style="text-align: center; max-width: 700px; margin: 0 auto;"&gt;&lt;img src="https://comiccaster.xyz/.netlify/functions/proxy-farside-image?url=https%3A%2F%2Ffeatureassets.amuniversal.com%2Fassets%2F4dba17d0d7420137c8a6005056a9545d" alt="The Far Side comic" style="max-width: 100%; height: auto;"/&gt;&lt;/div&gt;&lt;p style="margin-top: 10px; font-style: italic;"&gt;“There! Quick, Larry! Look! … Was I kidding? … That sucker’s longer than the boat!”&lt;/p&gt;&lt;p style="margin-top: 15px; font-size: 0.9em;"&gt;&lt;a href="https://www.thefarside.com/"&gt;Visit The Far Side&lt;/a&gt; | © Gary Larson&lt;/p&gt;</description><guid isPermaLink="false">https://www.thefarside.com/2026/07/09/0</guid><pubDate>Thu, 09 Jul 2026 08:05:00 -0400</pubDate></item><item><title>The Far Side - 2026-07-08 #5</title><link>https://www.thefarside.com/2026/07/08/4</link><description>&lt;div style="text-align: center; max-width: 700px; margin: 0 auto;"&gt;&lt;img src="https://comiccaster.xyz/.netlify/functions/proxy-farside-image?url=https%3A%2F%2Ffeatureassets.amuniversal.com%2Fassets%2F9d56eaf0963101395e72005056a9545d" alt="The Far Side comic" style="max-width: 100%; height: auto;"/&gt;&lt;/div&gt;&lt;p style="margin-top: 10px; font-style: italic;"&gt;“Remember, milk, eggs, loaf of bread … and pick up one of those No-Penguin-Strips.”&lt;/p&gt;&lt;p style="margin-top: 15px; font-size: 0.9em;"&gt;&lt;a href="https://www.thefarside.com/"&gt;Visit The Far Side&lt;/a&gt; | © Gary Larson&lt;/p&gt;</description><guid isPermaLink="false">https://www.thefarside.com/2026/07/08/4</guid><pubDate>Wed, 08 Jul 2026 08:04:00 -0400</pubDate></item><item><title>The Far Side - 2026-07-08 #4</title><link>https://www.thefarside.com/2026/07/08/3</link>